        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) Dum in Dei nomine locus qui dicitur <placeName key="#Assembly"
                            ref="#places/1537">Farfingo</placeName><rs key="#Iudiciaria">
                            <geogName key="#Iudiciaria #Assembly" ref="#estates/1110"
                                >iudiciaria</geogName>
                        </rs><placeName key="#Iudiciaria #Comitatus #Assembly" ref="#places/9"
                            >Bresia[nensi]</placeName> . . . .eorum data licencia in <rs
                            key="#Assembly">iudicio resideret</rs> domnus <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Count #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Camera_regis #Comitatus #Assembly #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#people/2122">Teudaldus</persName><rs key="#Marquis/duke">
                            marchio</rs> et <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> ipsius <geogName
                            ref="#estates/312" key="#Count"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatus</rs>
                            Bresianense</geogName> unicuique iusticias faciendas et deliberandas,
                        residentibus cum eo <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"
                                ><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Eribertus"
                                >Eriberto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Gundalpertus"
                                >Gundelbertus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Teutius"
                                >Teuzo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Autecheri"
                                >Autegerius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Adaldus"
                                >Adoaldus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Ermericus"
                                >Ermericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge">iudices sacri palacii</rs>,
                            <persName key="#vassusOf"><name ref="Ildefosulus"
                            >Ildefosulo</name></persName>, <persName key="#vassusOf"><name
                                ref="Ardoinus">Ardoino</name></persName>, <persName key="#vassusOf"
                                ><name ref="Raginardus">Raginardo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#vassusOf"><name ref="Adam">Adame</name>,</persName>
                        <persName key="#vassusOf"><name ref="Frogerius">Frugero</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#vassusOf"><name ref="Gherardus"
                            >Girardo</name></persName>, <persName key="#vassusOf"><name ref="Wido"
                                >Vuido</name></persName>, <persName key="#vassusOf"><name
                                ref="Sichinzo">Sigezo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#vassusOf">vassis</rs> suprascripti Teudaldi marchio et comes et
                        reliqui plures. Ibique eorum veniens presencia <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities" ref="#people/1232"
                            >Atho</persName> filius quondam <persName><name ref="Everardus"
                                >Everardi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">avocato</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Camera_of_other_public_authorities #Churches #Monasteries"
                                ><placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15">Sancti
                                Silvestri</placeName></orgName> et rettulit: 'Tam plures vices me
                        reclamavit ad vos, domnus Teudaldus marchio et comes istius comitatu
                        Bresianense, super <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/1233">Boso</persName>
                        comes filius quondam <persName ref="#people/1234">Manfredi</persName>, qui
                        mihi a pars ipsius <rs key="#Monasteries">abacia</rs> sancti Silvestri malo
                        ordine et contra lege detinent ac contradicent <rs key="#Churches"
                            >capella</rs> una, qui est in loco ubi dicitur a <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Churches" ref="#places/1504"
                            >Solara</placeName>, qui est consecrata in onore <orgName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1105"
                            >sancte Marie virginis</orgName>, una simul cum <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis masariciis</rs> et omnibus rebus
                        a dicta capella pertinentibus, unde vos, donus Teutaldus marchio et comes,
                        da vestra parte plures <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >misos</rs> direxistis, ut ipse Boso ad vestrum placitum veniset et
                        michi a pars ipsius abacia sancti Silvestri de iam dicta capella cum omnibus
                        rebus a se pertinentibus iusticiam fecisset, set minime eum ad vestrum
                        placitum abere potuistis. Unde quero, ut vos, donus Teutaldus marchio et
                        comes, propter Deum et anime donni inperatoris ac vestre mercedis me a pars
                        ipsius monesterio sancti Silvestri de eadem capella cum omnibus rebus a se
                        pertinentibus salva querela investiatis cousque ipse Boso ad placitum veniad
                        et michi a pars ipsius monesterii iusticiam faciadâ€™. Cum ipse Atho avocatus
                        taliter retulisset, ad hec ipse donnus Teudaldus marchio et comes recordatus
                        dixit, quod plures misos eidem Bosoni comes ex sua parte diresiset, ut ipse
                        Boso comes ad suum placitum veniset, et eidem Athoni avocatus a parte ipsius
                        monesterio sancti Silvestri de iam dicta capella cum omnibus a se
                        pertinentibus iusticiam fecisset, set minime eum ad suum placitum abere
                        potuit. Cum ipse donnus Teudaldus marchio et comes taliter retuliset, tunc
                        per fustem quam suam tenebat manu eodem Atho avocato sancti Silvestri de
                        eadem capella cum omnibus rebus a se pertinentibus a pars ipsius monesterio
                        sancti Silvestri salva querela investivit cousque ipse Boso comes ad
                        placitum veniad et eidem Athoni avocatus a parte ipsius monesterii iusticiam
                        faciad. Insuper misit <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">bannum</rs>
                        donni inperatoris in mancusos aureos mille, ut nulla magna parvaque persona
                        eundem Atho et pars ipsius monesterii sancti Silvestri sine legali iudicio
                        devestire audead. Qui vero fecerit, predictos mille mancusos aureos
                        conpositurus se anoscat, medietatem parti <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere
                            donni inperatoris</rs> et medietatem <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">pars ipsius abacia sancti
                            Silvestri</rs>. Et anc noticia, qualiter acta est, fieri admonuerunt.
                        Quidem et ego <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Aginus"
                            >Agino</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> ex iussione suprascripti Teudaldi marchio et
                        comes seu <rs key="#Placitum/iudicatum">iudicum amonetione scrisi</rs>. Anno
                        donni <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #Camera_regis #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#people/7">Ottoni</persName> tercio <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >inperator</rs> augustus anno inperii eius Deo propicio ic in Italia
                        quinto, sesto kalendas februarii, indicione quartadecima. Teudaldus marchio
                            <rs key="#Witness">subscripsi</rs>. (S) Petrus iudex sacri palacii
                        interfui. (S) Eribertus iudex sacri palacii interfuit. (S) Adoaldus iudex
                        sacri palacii interfui. (S) Teuzo iudex sacri palacii interfui. (S)
                        Atecherius iudex sacri palatii interfui. (S) Gundelbertus iudex sacri
                        palatii interfui.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
